  supplier_contact STRING
);

  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,

);

  supplier_name STRING,
  supplier_contact STRING
);

CREATE TABLE products (
  product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name STRING,
  quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
  customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_name STRING,
  customer_contact STRING
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  order_date DATE,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id)
);

CREATE TABLE categories (
  category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  category_name STRING
);</t><s>insert into categories (category_id, category_name) select 1, 'category1'</s>

  supplier_name STRING,
  supplier_contact STRING
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  order_date DATE,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id)
);

  category_name STRING

  order_date DATE,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id)
);

  supplier_name STRING,
  supplier_contact STRING
);

  customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_name STRING,
  customer_contact STRING
);

  product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name STRING,
  quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  order_date DATE,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id)

  customer_name STRING,
  customer_contact STRING
);
